data.description: Private, peaceful, and plenty of room to grow in this Mount Pleasant home with almost 4 acres! Desirable open concept living with a family room featuring a beautiful stone fireplace, and a spacious kitchen with tons of cabinets for storage, refrigerator, and electric stove. Have Sunday suppers in your formal dining room with wonderful laminate floors. The large primary suite has carpet floors with ample closet space, and a bathroom with a single sink vanity, and a standing shower. There are two nice size guest bedrooms with laminate floors, ceiling fans, and good closet space. The guest bathroom has a single sink vanity with a shower/tub combination. Have the party at your place with a huge deck for grilling, and a lush green backyard with mature trees for privacy. Bring your imagination and create your very own family compound in charming Mount Pleasant!
